Name: Super GunWorld 2
About the game: Upgraded with improved visuals and checkpoints, as well as other difficulty rebalances and polish. The sequel no one asked for, to the game that nobody liked! The Exaction Faction, an intergalactic troupe of super heroes, has come to arrest President Eagle! Explore GunWorld to level up, collect new gear, and hunt down the Faction members in this retro-inspired action/platformer/RPG hybrid.
